ivardefs.name: binding
ivardefs.desc: Binds to a value set if this parameter is coded (code, Coding, CodeableConcept).

ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: Describes the meaning or use of this parameter.

ivardefs.name: max
ivardefs.desc: The maximum number of times this element is permitted to appear in the request or response.

ivardefs.name: min
ivardefs.desc: The minimum number of times this parameter SHALL appear in the request or response.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: The name of used to identify the parameter.

ivardefs.name: profile
ivardefs.desc: A profile the specifies the rules that this parameter must conform to.

ivardefs.name: searchType
ivardefs.desc: How the parameter is understood as a search parameter. This is only used if the parameter type is 'string'.

ivardefs.name: use
ivardefs.desc: Whether this is an input or an output parameter.
